add a new modifier True Nightmare
After the enemys wake up, A image of TerrorBlade will chase them for the duration of Fear, the Image deals 60% 90% 120% 150% of
terrorBlade damage. If the Image Kill their Victims, It will return to TerrorBlade giving him 2% movement speed up to 30%
if TerrorBlade dies he will lose all of this bonus and if he gets to 30% he will gain 10% increase damage with 5% spell amp

SPELL W Sunder
Steal the life from the target dealing Max health damage to them and giving their own life to TerroBlade. For every Life TerrorBlade
Steal he will gain bonus Armor and Magic Resist with Movement Speed and if he kill his Target he will gain Life Bonus from his Target
with no Duration but if he goes into True Form he will lose that life bonus. While in Normal Form increase the max life damage by 7%
for normal units and bosses by 2% and reducing the cooldown by 50%

damage 6% 10% 14% 18% of Max health
bosses Damage 1% 2% 3% 4% of Max Health
life needed for bonus 40 50 60 70
magic resist per life Stolen 1% 2% 3% 4%
Armor per life Stolen 0.3 0.7 1.1 1.5
movement speed per life Stolen 4 8 12 16 FLAT
Duration of Life Stolen Buff 8 second
Life Bonus from the target 10% 15% 20% 25% of the target total max Health
cooldown 30 28 26 24
mana cost 80 100 120 140 plus 2% of max mana

Talent level 10 upgrade Sunder
reduce life needed for bonus by 20
increase movement speed bonus by 4
increase life bonus from enemys by 15%

add a new modifier Soul Breaker
After Casting Sunder on a, they will start to lose 1% of their max life per second 0.2% on bosses, for 10 second and TerrorBlade will
gain that life they lose. If the target dies under Soul Breaker he will Explode healing TerrorBlade for 5% of his Max health and he
will Spread Suol Breaker on other Target for the Same amount of duration but dealing 0.5% more Life damage on them, Bosses are
immune to the Spreads. enemys affected by Soul Breaker will have 25% healing reduction


